  <summary date="2020-04-23T21:35:19Z" status="Introduced in House">Apprenticeship Hubs Across America Act of 2019

This bill requires the Department of Labor to implement a program to award grants to workforce intermediaries (certain national, regional, state, or local entities that facilitate the establishment of registered apprenticeship programs) to enable them to engage a variety of stakeholders to support, develop, and implement registered apprenticeship programs.</summary>
